      <title>政治低迷导致法国消费者信心指数意外下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/french-consumer-sentiment-unexpectedly-falls-amid-political-gloom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国12月份消费者信心意外跌至一年来最低水平，进一步表明该国长期的政治和预算危机正在影响经济前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/french-consumer-sentiment-unexpectedly-falls-amid-political-gloom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 07:58:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反歧视顾问敦促德国政府退出 X</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/german-government-urged-to-quit-x-by-antidiscrimination-adviser</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国独立反歧视专员敦促政府关闭其 X 账户，称伊隆马斯克拥有的社交媒体平台已成为“世界首富的政治影响工具”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/german-government-urged-to-quit-x-by-antidiscrimination-adviser</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 06:17:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将在预算中简化已实施数十年的所得税申报规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/india-to-simplify-decades-old-income-tax-filing-rules-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府计划简化所得税申报规则，使纳税人遵守法律的难度降低，并有助于减少过去十年间激增至 1200 多亿美元的纠纷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/india-to-simplify-decades-old-income-tax-filing-rules-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 06:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sejourne 表示，特朗普上任后，欧盟不能掉以轻心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/eu-can-t-risk-complacency-ahead-of-trump-sejourne-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着当选总统唐纳德·特朗普本月晚些时候重返白宫，欧盟必须做好准备，以抵御美国新政府可能采取的惩罚性贸易措施。这是新任欧盟委员会副主席、欧盟工业战略负责人斯特凡纳·塞约尔内 (Stéphane Séjourné) 在布鲁塞尔接受彭博社奥利弗·克鲁克 (Oliver Crook) 独家采访时所说的。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/eu-can-t-risk-complacency-ahead-of-trump-sejourne-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 05:01:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业负责人表示，特朗普上台前，欧盟不能掉以轻心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/eu-can-t-risk-complacency-ahead-of-trump-industry-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟工业领袖表示，欧盟必须做好准备，抵御其他国家的贸易保护主义措施，包括唐纳德·特朗普本月晚些时候返回白宫后采取的任何新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/eu-can-t-risk-complacency-ahead-of-trump-industry-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 05:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克支持特朗普后，在欧洲采取“刀耕火种”的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/elon-musk-s-political-interventions-in-uk-germany-put-targets-on-back-foot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位世界首富将目光瞄准了德国、英国和欧盟的监管权力。]]></description>
