    <item>
      <title>韩国因尹永哲被捕而引发的僵局可能演变为暴力冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/south-korean-standoff-over-yoon-s-arrest-risks-violent-turn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国被弹劾的领导人被困在首尔的住所内，受到巴士、铁丝网、支持者人群和他自己的武装保安人员的保护。现在的问题是调查人员能否在不发生暴力冲突的情况下逮捕他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/south-korean-standoff-over-yoon-s-arrest-risks-violent-turn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 03:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国弹劾总统面临第二次逮捕威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/impeached-south-korean-president-yoon-faces-second-arrest-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国反腐败监督机构已获得延长逮捕被弹劾总统尹锡烈的逮捕令，并且最早可能在周三第二次试图拘留这位陷入困境的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/impeached-south-korean-president-yoon-faces-second-arrest-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 23:37:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对格陵兰的执着让丹麦成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-s-relentless-greenland-fixation-puts-denmark-in-spotlight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对丹麦的格陵兰岛一直念念不忘，他需要反复提醒这位回国的总统，世界上最大的岛屿是非卖品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-s-relentless-greenland-fixation-puts-denmark-in-spotlight</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普中东特使称与哈马斯的人质协议即将达成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-envoy-to-middle-east-says-hostage-deal-with-hamas-is-close</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普即将任命的中东问题特使表示，谈判人员即将达成协议，以确保释放哈马斯在与以色列的战争中劫持的人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-envoy-to-middle-east-says-hostage-deal-with-hamas-is-close</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:23:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
